Package: roc
Type: Package
Title: Working With Ocean Colour Data
Version: 0.0.9
Authors@R: c(person("Michael D.","Sumner", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "mdsumner@gmail.com"), 
             person("Norman", "Kuring", role = "ctb", comment = "Author of L3bin code (NASA)"), 
             person("Robert Johnson", role = "ctb", comment = "Developed southern ocean algorithm for chlorophyll"))
Description: Work with data from NASA's ocean colour data, primarily the 'Level-3 bin' 
  files. There are functions to read from these files, deal with the ragged array 'L3 bins'
  mesh and calculate biophysical properties from radiance values. 
License: GPL-3
LazyLoad: yes
Depends: dplyr
